-- üèÉ ‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ß (‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏°‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏°)
local Players = game:GetService("Players")
local player = Players.LocalPlayer
local PlayerGui = player:WaitForChild("PlayerGui")

-- ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á GUI ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏Å
local ScreenGui = Instance.new("ScreenGui")
ScreenGui.Name = "SpeedMenu"
ScreenGui.ResetOnSpawn = false
ScreenGui.Parent = PlayerGui

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π (‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏Ç‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏ö‡∏ô)
local OpenButton = Instance.new("TextButton")
OpenButton.Name = "OpenButton"
OpenButton.Size = UDim2.new(0, 100, 0, 40)
OpenButton.Position = UDim2.new(1, -110, 0, 10)
OpenButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 0, 0)
OpenButton.Text = "‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π"
OpenButton.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
OpenButton.TextScaled = true
OpenButton.Parent = ScreenGui

-- ‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
local MenuFrame = Instance.new("Frame")
MenuFrame.Name = "MenuFrame"
MenuFrame.Size = UDim2.new(0, 220, 0, 130)
MenuFrame.Position = UDim2.new(0.5, -110, 0.5, -65)
MenuFrame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 0, 0)
MenuFrame.Visible = false
MenuFrame.Parent = ScreenGui
MenuFrame.BorderSizePixel = 2
MenuFrame.Active = true
MenuFrame.Draggable = true  -- ‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ

local Title = Instance.new("TextLabel")
Title.Parent = MenuFrame
Title.Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 40)
Title.Text = "‚ö° ‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ß ‚ö°"
Title.BackgroundTransparency = 1
Title.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
Title.TextScaled = true

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î/‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ß
local SpeedButton = Instance.new("TextButton")
SpeedButton.Parent = MenuFrame
SpeedButton.Size = UDim2.new(0.8, 0, 0, 40)
SpeedButton.Position = UDim2.new(0.1, 0, 0.5, -20)
SpeedButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 80, 80)
SpeedButton.Text = "‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ß"
SpeedButton.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
SpeedButton.TextScaled = true

-- ‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
local CloseButton = Instance.new("TextButton")
CloseButton.Parent = MenuFrame
CloseButton.Size = UDim2.new(0.3, 0, 0, 30)
CloseButton.Position = UDim2.new(0.65, 0, 0, 10)
CloseButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(200, 0, 0)
CloseButton.Text = "‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î"
CloseButton.TextColor3 = Color3.new(1, 1, 1)
CloseButton.TextScaled = true

-- ====== Logic ======
local menuOpen = false
local speedOn = false
local defaultSpeed = 16

-- ‡∏Å‡∏î‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
OpenButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	menuOpen = not menuOpen
	MenuFrame.Visible = menuOpen
end)

-- ‡∏Å‡∏î‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π "‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ß"
SpeedButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	local char = player.Character or player.CharacterAdded:Wait()
	local humanoid = char:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid")
	if not humanoid then return end

	if not speedOn then
		humanoid.WalkSpeed = 100
		speedOn = true
		SpeedButton.Text = "‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ß"
		SpeedButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 255, 0)
	else
		humanoid.WalkSpeed = defaultSpeed
		speedOn = false
		SpeedButton.Text = "‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ß"
		SpeedButton.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 80, 80)
	end
end)

-- ‡∏Å‡∏î‡∏õ‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏π
CloseButton.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
	menuOpen = false
	MenuFrame.Visible = false
end)
